INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('The freshest summer tomatoes shine in this five-ingredient supper.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Pick from chicken breast or thighs to build these smoky skewers. Who doesnt love dinner on a stick?!');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Put your bumper crop to good use by mixing spiralized zucchini with spaghetti. Sauteed chicken ups the protein.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('A vibrant herby sauce does double duty as a marinade and a drizzle on top of this fresh summer chicken dinner.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This one-pan meal combines chicken thighs  shiitake mushrooms and water chestnuts in a delicious hoisin-based sauce.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Toss protein-packed ingredients on a sheet pan to roast together  then add to a filling veggie bowl. Your stomach will thank you!');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Twenty minutes is all you need to whip up this feast. Smoked paprika adds richness while tomato and crisp lettuce boost freshness.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Homemade tahini plays up the earthy  toasty notes in the sumac-spiked marinade that serves as both a flavor-booster for the chicken and a delicious dressing to drizzle over cucumber-tomato salad.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Ras El Hanout gives this chicken recipe its floral brightness.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('For a beautifully golden exterior  we sear the chicken before nestling it on the sheet pan with the vegetables to finish roasting in the oven.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('The air fryer does it all: from crisping up the breaded chicken cutlets to heating the sauce and cheese to bubbling perfection.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Creamy herby feta is the perfect sauce to pair with spiced chicken.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Your air fryer is the perfect appliance to use on the hottest summer days. It wont heat up your kitchen like the oven and it produces crisp golden-brown chicken tenders.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Bookmark this recipe for when you want to make the most of your rotisserie chicken. Its simple and comforting  bringing together chicken  beans  tortillas and sauce.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('These veggie-packed sandwiches are a must-have for any summer picnic. They bring together grilled chicken and creamy Caesar dressing  all enclosed in a perfectly crusty baguette.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('For nights when its just too hot to cook  or even grill  turn to this light and satisfying recipe. In addition to shredded rotisserie chicken and snap peas  it brings together onion  mint  parsley and Parmesan.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This elegant meal is sure to impress anyone  whether youre having a dinner party with friends or whipping up something new for date night.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This is another recipe thats perfect for when its just too hot to turn on the oven. It all comes together in the rice cooker â€” yes  chicken included.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This spice rub inspired by tandoori masala adds something special to chicken and cauliflower. Creamy  cooling Greek yogurt and warmed naan take things to the next level. Get the Tandoori-Spiced Cauliflower Chicken Flatbreads recipe.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('A homemade Italian dressing infuses both the chicken and fresh veggies with bold flavor. Its a perfect lunch for those hot summer days.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('When its just too hot to turn on the oven or fire up the grill  the air fryer will be your best friend. These crowd-pleasing mini pizza pies feature pepperoncini and honey for that extra-special touch.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Nothing says summer quite like a refreshing cucumber salad tossed with a citrusy  salty dressing. Pair it with juicy steak for a satisfying and simple dinner. Though the recipe calls for your steak to be done in a cast-iron skillet  you could grill it if you prefer.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Got friends coming over for dinner? Whip up this dish thats both impressive and easy to make. It has plenty of fresh summer flavors thanks to the ginger-orange vinaigrette and crunchy sugar snap peas.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Need some meatless Monday inspiration? Wed recommend this palak paneer  a Northern Indian dish made with plenty of spinach and roasted paneer. Dont forget the rice and naan for serving!');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('If you ask us  theres never a wrong time for chicken parmesan when you can make it in the air fryer for easy cleanup.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This tasty dinner takes just five ingredients and less than an hour to make. The harissa-infused butter adds an appetizing complexity to an already delicious dinner of tender steak and roasted carrots.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This easy dinner brings together rotisserie chicken  canned sauce  and beans. It comes together quickly  so you can get back to relaxing and enjoying the summer evening.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Nothing says summer like roasted clams. Add the crunchy  lemony breadcrumbs to take things to the next level.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Talk about flavor! This recipe features skirt steak  rice noodles  mint  cilantro  lime  cucumber and more.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This recipe is great for days you cant bear to turn on the oven. Grilled chicken  creamy Caesar dressing and fresh veggies make for a refreshing and protein-packed dinner.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This bright  flavorful salad brings together plenty of fruits and veggies. Serve it as a side at your next backyard get-together  or enjoy it as a meal for two.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Grilled  smoky shrimp with an herbaceous rub and squeeze of lemon is basically the epitome of summer. Youll definitely want to add this to the rotation.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('The secret to 20-minute dinner is pre-toasting panko with a little bit of oil. Everyones going to want seconds of these Japanese-inspired pork cutlets.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Its not officially summer until you serve up a plate of these simple but delicious ribs  which are baked and then finished on the grill with barbecue sauce.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This delicate fish is simmered in a little bit of along with tomatoes  garlic  olives and a few other ingredients. You might as well pour a glass of rosÃ© to enjoy alongside this easy dinner!');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Trust us  the kids are going to love this one. I mean  pizza dough  ground beef  veggies  and barbecue sauce â€” whats not to love?');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Any standout summer dinner starts with a perfect grilled steak. Pair it with an herby farro salad to round out the meal.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Keep a batch of homemade marinated peppers (best made with in-season summer peppers!) on hand to whip up this pasta in a flash.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Got a garden full of zucchini? Put them to delicious use in this five-ingredient dinner.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Coat chicken breast in cornflakes for a crispy exterior without frying. A plate full of fresh lettuce and herbs keep this light enough for hot days!');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Pasta is included  of course! This lifestyle emphasizes integrating more whole grains into your routine  so feel free to swap in whole-wheat noodles. For an extra nutrition boost  toss in some zoodles.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('This low-calorie option doesnt compromise on satisfaction or flavor to a ton of produce (hello  caramelized onions  fennel and juicy tomatoes!)  plus a sprinkle of sumac.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Youll want to memorize this side recipe: the combo of couscous  cucumbers  feta and fresh herbs can go with so many mains.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('Hear us out: You can (and should!) make a complete meal in your rice cooker. The chicken cooks on the steamer rack above the grains  and everything is done at the same time.');
INSERT INTO label (label_description) VALUES ('The beauty of the Mediterranean Diet is that while you are featuring fish and lean proteins more often  you dont have to explicitly say "no" to meats like lamb.');
